      "content": "\"Moving forward and self-care can feel impossible when you're feeling this way, but it's important to remember that it's never too late to seek help. Sometimes, finding peace doesn't come easily, and that's okay. There are people who can support you through this tough time and help you find a way to cope. Remember, you're not alone in this, and it's okay to ask for help when you need it. It's important to take things one step at a time and be kind to yourself during this difficult period.\"",
      "source": "target",
